ed="T" n="0792b25"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0792b25"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042139"><placeName>京師</placeName><placeName>恒濟寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A001899">懷素</persName>傳（<persName key="A000614">賓<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0792b26"/><persName key="A001899">釋懷素</persName>，姓<name>范</name>氏，其先<placeName key="PL000000025497">南陽</placeName>人也。曾祖<persName key="A010787">嶽</persName>，<persName key="A002146">高宗</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0792b27"/>朝選調<ptr type="glossary" target="#g160"/>為<placeName key="PL000000005740"><placeName>絳州</placeName><placeName>曲沃縣</placeName></placeName>丞。祖<persName key="A010788">徽</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000043600"><placeName>延州</placeName><placeName>廣武縣</placeName></placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0792b28"/>令。父<persName key="A010789">強</persName>，左武衛長史，乃為<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>人也。母<persName key="A019329">李<lb
ed="T" n="0792b29"/><roleName>氏</roleName></persName>夢雲雷震駭，因而娠焉。誕育之辰，神光滿<pb ed="T" n="0792c" xml:id="T50.2061.0792c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792c01"/>室。見者求占：<ref type="person" target="#A001899">此子</ref>貴極，當為王者之師傅<lb
ed="T" n="0792c02"/>也。幼齡聰黠，器度寬然，識者曰：「學必成功，才<lb
ed="T" n="0792c03"/>當逸格<ptr type="glossary" target="#g159"/>。」耳聞口誦，皆謂老成<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g672"/>。年及<date key="j19559111956275" from-iso="+0643-01-01" to-iso="+0643-12-31">十歲</date>，忽<lb
ed="T" n="0792c04"/>發出家之意，猛利之性，<ref type="person" target="#A010789 #A019329">二親</ref>難沮。<date from-iso="+0645-02-05" key="j19566771957030" to-iso="+0646-01-24"><name>貞觀</name>十九<lb
ed="T" n="0792c05"/>年</date>，<persName key="A000294">玄奘<roleName>三藏</roleName></persName>方<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>迴，誓求為師。雲與龍而<lb
ed="T" n="0792c06"/>同物，星將<ptr type="glossary" target="#g38"/>月以共光，俱懸<name>釋</name>氏之天，悉麗<lb
ed="T" n="0792c07"/>著明之象<ptr type="glossary" target="#g161"/>。初尋經論，不費光陰。受具已來<ptr target="#n907"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0792c08"/>專攻律部。有<placeName key="PL000000024082">鄴郡</placeName><persName key="A000747">法礪<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，一方名器，五律<ptr type="glossary" target="#g163"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792c09"/>宗師，迷方皆俟其指南，得路咸推其鄉導。<lb
ed="T" n="0792c10"/>著疏十卷<ptr target="#n903"/>，別是命家<ptr type="glossary" target="#g162"/>。見接<persName key="A001899">素<roleName>公</roleName></persName>，知成律匠<ptr target="#n2791"/>。研<lb
ed="T" n="0792c11"/>習三載，乃見諸瑕，喟然歎曰：「古人義章，未能<lb
ed="T" n="0792c12"/>盡善！」<date from-iso="+0670-03-30" key="j19658611966185" to-iso="+0671-02-17"><name>咸亨</name>元年</date>，發起勇心，別述《開四分律<lb
ed="T" n="0792c13"/>記》<ptr target="#n902"/>。至<date from-iso="+0676-01-24" key="j19679871968318" to-iso="+0676-12-20"><name>上元</name>三年丙子</date>歸<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京</ref>，奉詔住<placeName key="PL000000042324">西太原<lb
ed="T" n="0792c14"/>寺</placeName>傍聽<persName key="A008984">道成<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>講<ptr target="#n908"/>，不輟緝綴。<date from-iso="+0682-04-05" key="j19702501970555" to-iso="+0683-02-04"><name>永淳</name>元年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0792c15"/>十軸畢功，一家新立<ptr target="#n904"/>，彈糾古疏，十有六失<lb
ed="T" n="0792c16"/>焉。新義半千百條也。傅翼之彪，搏攫而有知<lb
ed="T" n="0792c17"/>皆畏；乘風之震，砰輷而無遠不聞。所化翕<lb
ed="T" n="0792c18"/>然，所傳多矣。復著《俱舍論疏》一十五卷，《遺教<lb
ed="T" n="0792c19"/>經疏》二卷，《鈔》三卷，《新疏拾遺鈔》二十卷，《四分僧<lb
ed="T" n="0792c20"/>尼羯磨文》兩卷<ptr target="#n2790"/>，《四分僧尼戒本》各一卷。日誦<lb
ed="T" n="0792c21"/>《金剛經》三十卷，講大律已疏<ptr target="#n902"/>計五十餘遍，其<lb
ed="T" n="0792c22"/>餘書經、畫像，不可勝數。於本寺別院忽示<lb
ed="T" n="0792c23"/>疾，力且薾然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g165"/>，告<persName key="A019330">秀章</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A001899">余</ref>律行多缺，一報<lb
ed="T" n="0792c24"/>將終。」時空中有天樂瀏亮，奄然而逝，俗齡<lb
ed="T" n="0792c25"/>七十四，法臘五十三。葬日，有鴻鶴遶塔悲<lb
ed="T" n="0792c26"/>鳴，至暮方散。<persName key="A001899">素</persName>所撰述，宗薩婆多<ptr target="#n882"/>，何邪？<lb
ed="T" n="0792c27"/>以法密部緣化地部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g166"/>出，化地從有部<ptr type="glossary" target="#g244"/>生，故出受<lb
ed="T" n="0792c28"/>體<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1231"/>以無表色<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1278"/>也。又斥二宗云：「<persName key="A000747">相部</persName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2176"/>無知，則<lb
ed="T" n="0792c29"/>大開量中，得自取大小行也<ptr target="#n910"/>。<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>犯重，則<pb ed="T" n="0793a" xml:id="T50.2061.0793a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0793a01"/>與天神言論，是自言得上人法也<ptr target="#n911"/>。」大抵<persName key="A001899">素</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0793a02"/>疏出，謂之「新章」焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0713-12-26" key="j19818371992113" notAfter-iso="+0742-02-13"><name>開元</name>中</date>，<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName><persName key="A000614">賓<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>造《飾<lb
ed="T" n="0793a03"/>宗記》<ptr target="#n912"/>以解釋之，對<persName key="A000747">礪</persName>舊疏也。又謂為東、西<lb
ed="T" n="0793a04"/>塔律宗，因傳習處為名耳。<date notBefore-iso="+0766-12-22" key="j20011912005747" notAfter-iso="+0779-06-13"><name>大曆</name>中</date>，相國<persName key="A010790">元<lb
ed="T" n="0793a05"/><roleName>公</roleName>載</persName>奏<placeName key="PL000000034768"><placeName>成都</placeName><placeName>寶園寺</placeName></placeName>置戒壇，傳新疏，以俸<lb
ed="T" n="0793a06"/>錢寫疏四十本，《法華經疏》三十本，委<placeName key="PL000000034768">寶園</placeName><persName key="A010791">光<lb
ed="T" n="0793a07"/>翌</persName>傳行之。後<persName key="A010790">元<roleName>公</roleName></persName>命<persName key="A010792">如淨<roleName>公</roleName></persName>為<persName key="A001899">素</persName>作傳。<persName key="A004370">韋<lb
ed="T" n="0793a08"/><persName>南康</persName>皋</persName>作靈壇，傳授毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>新《疏記》，有承襲<lb
ed="T" n="0793a09"/>者，刊名于石。其辭酋麗，其翰兼美，為<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>中<lb
ed="T" n="0793a10"/>口實<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1325"/>焉。</p>
